                     <interp inst="t18010415-93-defend983" type="age" value="23"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t18010415-93-off522" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010415-93-off522" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010415-93-off522" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the 16th of March, twenty yards of Irish cloth, value 42s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18010415-93-victim985" type="victimName">
                           Harrison 
                           Jackson
                        <interp inst="t18010415-93-victim985" type="surname" value="Jackson"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18010415-93-victim985" type="given" value="Harrison"></interp>
